							<locus from="1r" to="361v"/>
							<title xml:lang="he-Latn-x-lc">Pardes ha-ḥokhmah : perush ha-Torah be-῾iḳar ῾al derekh ha-ḳabalah</title>
							<title xml:lang="he">פרדס החכמה : פרוש התורה בעיקר על דרך הקבלה</title>
							<filiation>Cf. <ref target="Neubauer_1994" type="number">1919</ref>.</filiation>
							<note>
								<p>The commentary is largely made up of quotations from the Zohar (mostly in Hebrew), the Talmud, midrashim, Joseph Gikatilla's Sha῾are orah, Abraham Saba's Tseror ḥamor, etc.</p>
								<p>The commentary on Exodus begins on folio 150r; on Leviticus, folio 216r; on Numbers, folio 258v; on Deuteronomy, folio 333r.</p>
								<p>See also <ref target="Ale_sefer" type="number">9</ref> (1981), pp. 91-96.</p>
							</note>
						</msItem>
